                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960217-5-off22 t17960217-5-cd23"></join>, a cotton gown, value 10s. a duffield cloak, value 15s. and a cotton shawl, value 4s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17960217-5-victim86" type="victimName">
                     James 
